OL,3,CWhat is Palestine Action, and what
OL,4,Cdoes the High Court ruling mean?
OL,6,FPalestine Action has won a High Court
OL,7,Fchallenge against the ban of the
OL,8,Forganisation as a terror group on two
OL,9,Fgrounds.
OL,11,FOn Friday, the High Court ruled the
OL,12,Fgovernment's decision to ban the
OL,13,Fnetwork as a terror group was unlawful
OL,14,Fand "disproportionate", and should be
OL,15,Foverturned.
OL,17,FThe ban remains in place for now, and
OL,18,Fthe government is likely to appeal the
OL,19,Fruling.
