OL,3,CWhat is Palestine Action, and what
OL,4,Cdoes the High Court ruling mean?
OL,6,FThe group was created in 2020, when
OL,7,Fprotestors broke into the London
OL,8,Fheadquarters of Israel-based defence
OL,9,Ffirm Elbit Systems, covering the
OL,10,Fbuilding in red paint.
OL,12,FFounded by Huda Ammori and Richard
OL,13,FBarnard, the network reportedly has
OL,14,F20,000 people on its mailing list.
OL,16,FThe organisation describes itself as
OL,17,F"a direct action movement committed to
OL,18,Fending global participation in
OL,19,FIsrael's genocidal and apartheid
OL,20,Fregime.
