OL,3,CWhat is Palestine Action, and what
OL,4,Cdoes the High Court ruling mean?
OL,6,FIn Friday's High Court ruling, Dame
OL,7,FVictoria Sharp, sitting with Mr
OL,8,FJustice Swift and Mrs Justice Steyn,
OL,9,Fsaid: "We are satisfied that the
OL,10,Fdecision to proscribe Palestine Action
OL,11,Fwas disproportionate.
OL,13,F"At its core, Palestine Action is an
OL,14,Forganisation that promotes its
OL,15,Fpolitical cause through criminality
OL,16,Fand encouragement of criminality. A
OL,17,Fvery small number of its actions have
OL,18,Famounted to terrorist action."
