OL,6,FShe said: "The nature and scale of
OL,7,FPalestine Action's activities falling
OL,8,Fwithin the definition of terrorism had
OL,9,Fnot yet reached the level, scale and
OL,10,Fpersistence to warrant proscription."
OL,12,FConcluding her judgement, the judge
OL,13,Fproposed to make an order which will
OL,14,Fquash the decision to proscribe
OL,15,FPalestine Action. She clarified that
OL,16,Fthe group remains proscribed pending
OL,17,Flegal arguments over whether the
OL,18,Foverturning of the decision should be
OL,19,Fpaused.
